setting the SystemRegistryUI is good.

The other change I don't fully understand. Is it really sufficient if the parent is IAdaptable? Or would this bear the risk setting a parent that doesn't really work or is not compatible? At any rate, the change could be done more readable:

if (parent instanceof IAdaptable) {
    _parent = (IAdaptable) parent;
    setEnabled(true);
} else {
    _parent = null;
    setEnabled(false);
}
